		<article id="post-911" class="post-911 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized tag-construct tag-movies tag-presenz tag-virtual-reality tag-volumetric tag-volumetric-movies tag-vr">

            <div class="post-detail">
            	<!-- post title -->
				<h1 class="hide">
					<a href="https://www.presenzvr.com/use-cases/construct/" title="Construct">Construct</a>
				</h1>
				<!-- /post title -->
            	
                <!--<div class="meta">
			         
			        <span class="date"><span class="icon-Material-icons-03-61"></span>June 21, 2018 12:10 pm</span>
			        <span class="author"><span class="icon-Material-icons-08-91"></span>Published by <a href="https://www.presenzvr.com/use-cases/author/sten/" title="Posts by Sten Seghers" rel="author">Sten Seghers</a></span>
			        <span class="comments"><span class="icon-Material-icons-04-32"></span></span>
			         
                </div>-->
                <div class="content">
			        <div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="n2-section-smartslider "><div id="n2-ss-9-align" class="n2-ss-align n2-ss-align-visible" style="margin-left: -83.375px; width: 1026px;"><div class="n2-padding" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;"><div id="n2-ss-9" data-creator="Smart Slider 3" class="n2-ss-slider n2-ow n2-has-hover  n2-ss-load-fade n2-ss-desktop n2-ss-loaded" data-minfontsizedesktopportrait="1" data-minfontsizedesktoplandscape="1" data-minfontsizetabletportrait="10" data-minfontsizetabletlandscape="12" data-minfontsizemobileportrait="8" data-minfontsizemobilelandscape="10" style="font-size: 15.2px; width: 1026px; margin: 0px;" data-fontsize="16">
        <div class="n2-ss-slider-1 n2-ss-swipe-element n2-ow" style="width: 1026px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; height: 577px;">
                        <div class="n2-ss-slider-2 n2-ow">
                                <div class="n2-ss-slider-3 n2-ow" style="">

                    <div class="n2-ss-slide-backgrounds"><div class="n2-ss-slide-background n2-ow" data-mode="fit"><div class="n2-ss-slide-background-wrap n2-ow"><div data-hash="30f1a31928ad1ac0a8c23b85d1141fc2" data-desktop="//www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hand_SideWays_v03.jpg" class="n2-ss-slide-background-image" data-blur="0" style="background-image: url(&quot;//www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hand_SideWays_v03.jpg&quot;);"><noscript><img src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hand_SideWays_v03.jpg" alt="" /></noscript><img class="lazyload" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lqip,ret_wait/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hand_SideWays_v03.jpg" data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Hand_SideWays_v03.jpg" alt=""></div></div></div></div><div data-first="1" data-slide-duration="3" data-id="54" style="width: 1026px; height: 577px;" class="n2-ss-slide n2-ss-canvas n2-ow  n2-ss-slide-54 n2-ss-slide-active"><div class="n2-ss-layers-container n2-ow" data-csstextalign="center" style="width: 1026px; height: 577px; margin: 0px;"></div></div>                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        </div><div class="n2-clear"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid"><div class="text-white wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4 style="text-align: justify" class="vc_custom_heading">Construct VR</h4><div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_100 vc_sep_border_width_2 vc_sep_pos_align_center vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_white"><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span>
</div><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-2"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper"></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>“Construct” a short film by Kevin Margo, was originally a full CGI short movie for 2D screens. The PresenZ technology allowed us to reuse all the 3D scenes of Construct as they were, with the same models, lighting, textures, shaders, render engine ( V-Ray ), etc… We only had to clean-up some animation here and there, like foot contacts, since it was originally out of frame.</p>
<p>This illustrates that 3D assets designed for movies can be directly reused to create fully immersive VR content with PresenZ.</p>
<p>The experience of Construct itself begins when we are following a family of robots in their daily life routine. Bill, the father, works at a constructions site. After he says goodbye to his family he arrives at his workplace and stumbles upon something he should not have seen. As a viewer we are a bystander to the events that unfold.</p>

		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_video_widget wpb_content_element vc_clearfix   vc_video-aspect-ratio-169 vc_video-el-width-100 vc_video-align-left">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			
			<div class="wpb_video_wrapper"><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/471036442?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963&amp;h=36fd1d0dd8&amp;api=1&amp;player_id=vimeo_id_0" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" title="Construct VR - Teaser Trailer (PresenZ Volumetric Movie Format)" id="vimeo_id_0" data-gtm-yt-inspected-10842511_37="true"></iframe></div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h5>Construct Lumiere awards</h5>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_50 vc_sep_pos_align_left vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_white"><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span>
</div>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p>Construct won two Lumiere awards at Stereopsia 2018. “Best technical innovation in VR” for the use of the PresenZ technology and “Public choice awards”.</p>

		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left">
		
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><noscript><img width="960" height="540" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_960,h_540/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ffa04695-7131-4014-9862-61e8e147bda2-original-960x540.jpeg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-large" alt="Lumiere awards at stereopsia 2018" /></noscript><img width="960" height="540" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lqip,ret_wait,w_960,h_540/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ffa04695-7131-4014-9862-61e8e147bda2-original-960x540.jpeg" data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_960,h_540/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/ffa04695-7131-4014-9862-61e8e147bda2-original-960x540.jpeg" class="lazyload vc_single_image-img attachment-large" alt="Lumiere awards at stereopsia 2018"></div>
		</figure>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h5>Christophers (CEO at Stockaboo) comments</h5>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_50 vc_sep_pos_align_left vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_white"><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span>
</div>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><em>” I can say that this was one of the attractions that impressed me the most! The graphics are amazing and you really feel like you are at the construction site. Imagine the first time you experienced 3D cinema, it was quite impressive and a new type of experience. This is something completely different: a much bigger step! “</em></p>

		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left">
		
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><noscript><img width="700" height="467" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_700/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-large" alt="Stockaboo PresenZ Dubai" srcset="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_700/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct.jpg 700w, https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_480/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct-480x320.jpg 480w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><img width="700" height="467" src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lqip,ret_wait,w_700,h_467/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct.jpg" data-src="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_700/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct.jpg" class="lazyload vc_single_image-img attachment-large" alt="Stockaboo PresenZ Dubai" data-srcset="https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_700/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct.jpg 700w, https://sp-ao.shortpixel.ai/client/q_lossy,ret_img,w_480/https://www.presenzvr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Construct-480x320.jpg 480w" data-sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"></div>
		</figure>
	</div>

	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<h5>Mathias (Writer at Stockaboo) comments</h5>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="vc_separator wpb_content_element vc_separator_align_center vc_sep_width_50 vc_sep_pos_align_left vc_separator_no_text vc_sep_color_white"><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_l"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span><span class="vc_sep_holder vc_sep_holder_r"><span class="vc_sep_line"></span></span>
</div>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><em>“ PresenZ, PresenZ, PresenZ, what a movie! Robots fighting in a fight that would make any martial arts expert jealous. I have never experienced anything like that! Imagine mixing a 360 video with a pair of 3D glasses and then moving around in that world, then you have PresenZ.“</em></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Construct short film can be watched as an attraction at the classic old movie theater in Starbreeze and Emaar’s VR park in Dubai.</p>

		</div>
	</div>

<script type="text/javascript" id="">var dataLayer="undefined"!==typeof dataLayer&&dataLayer instanceof Array?dataLayer:[],videoLabels=[],lastP=[],_playerTitle={},_playerAuthor={},_playerAuthorURL={},_playerUploadDate={};try{init()}catch(a){dataLayer.push({event:"gtm.error",errorMessage:e.message,tag:"CP - UA - Vimeo Video Listener"})}
